message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to present our premium product to you. Given its high value and unique features, it's worth $15,000 to you. After careful consideration, we're offering this exceptional item to you for $14,000. This is a special opportunity to secure a high-quality product at a competitive price. We believe this offer presents a great value for both of us. Please let me know if you're interested in proceeding with this offer.
